snippet.title: The Sims 4 Romantic Garden Stuff: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Build a lush Victorian garden for your Sims to embrace romance and discover a bit of mystery in The Sims 4 Romantic Garden Stuff.
 
Learn more about this Stuff Pack: http://o.ea.com/51696
 
Visit the wishing well to see if your Sims’ deepest desires become reality or dress them in floral fashion to share a playful moment by the water fountain.
